## Get Maintenance Mode Info

```shell
$ curl 'https://ci.example.com/go/api/admin/maintenance_mode/info' \
-u 'username:password' \
-H 'Accept: <%= data.apis.versions.maintenance_mode %>'
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: <%= data.apis.versions.maintenance_mode %>; charset=utf-8
ETag: "cbc5f2d5b9c13a2cc1b1efb3d8a6155d"
```

